Cs_carpark
time to make: 4 weeks (on and off)
map info: 3 floors
               about 15 cars
               a collections of pitch black tunnels
               CT's start at entrance
               T's start on roof
               2 hosties per power room
               Blinding sun light on roof
               a few glitchly decals lol (dont moan about it)
               optimized as much as pos
               up to 32 players
               ive had complaints that its too big :S dunno if thats pos     for a css map but yea..
thats about it, enjoy :P
